Class SpfToGreenVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nasa.jpf.symbc.veritesting.ast.transformations.SPFCases.SpfToGreenVisitor

    AstVisitor<za.ac.sun.cs.green.expr.Expression>

    public class SpfToGreenVisitor
extends java.lang.Object
implements AstVisitor<za.ac.sun.cs.green.expr.Expression>
    Main visitor that visits all statements and translate them to the appropriate green expression. At the point the expected statements are, assignments, composition and skip.
